      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8 with eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is in showroom condition, boasting a pristine carbon fiber roof, a precise 6-speed manual transmission, and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Mechanically flawless with a comprehensive service history, the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides exceptional chassis response and damping precision. Truly a turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast seeking peak longitudinal and lateral performance in a concours-level specimen.",
