      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is an absolute gem\u2014it's been pampered since day one and honestly still feels like it just rolled off the lot. No scratches, no dings, just pure perfection inside and out. It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person! If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
