    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in a concours-level state. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced for long-term structural rigidity. It retains its factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock and original suspension geometry. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a factory-fresh interior, this M3 offers the tactile precision and high-revving engagement that defined an era of German engineering.",
